While we service these cars regularly and the engine is in ship shape, they do have 10-15 years of wear and tear so some have imperfections on interior/exterior. I do my best to keep each cars profile updated with pictures of any damage that way you can decide before booking whether you will be satisfied with the car or not. 

 Relationships are important to me, so I will do my best to see repeat customers.  If you ever have an issue, I guarantee that I will  address it ASAP and make things right, you can reach out 24/7 with any questions or concerns. 

Thank You for your interest .
